### Start Session Recording
# Creates a new session replay recording for an in-app feature

POST https://api.costkatana.com/api/session-replay/recording/start
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{API_KEY}}

{
  "userId": "user_12345",
  "feature": "chat",
  "label": "Customer Support Chat - 2025-10-28"
}

### Expected Response
# {
#   "success": true,
#   "data": {
#     "sessionId": "inapp_chat_1234567890_abc123"
#   }
# }

